library(ggplot2)
library(dplyr)
agg <- function(num_var = 10, PSR = 0.05, dist = 5,dist2 = 5, type = "type1"){
    gmm = read.csv(paste0(type,"/var",num_var,"/var",num_var,"_c",dist2,"/final_gmm_c",dist,"_var",num_var,"_ARI_10_PSR",PSR,".csv"), col.names = c("dataset_index","ARI","Accuracy"))
    prkm = read.csv(paste0(type,"/var",num_var,"/var",num_var,"_c",dist2,"/final_prkm_c",dist,"_var",num_var,"_ARI_10_PSR",PSR,".csv"), col.names = c("dataset_index","ARI","Accuracy"))
    rkm = read.csv(paste0(type,"/var",num_var,"/var",num_var,"_c",dist2,"/final_rkm_c",dist,"_var",num_var,"_ARI_10_PSR",PSR,".csv"), col.names = c("dataset_index","ARI","Accuracy"))
    km = read.csv(paste0(type,"/var",num_var,"/var",num_var,"_c",dist2,"/final_kmeans_c",dist,"_var",num_var,"_ARI_10_PSR",PSR,".csv"), col.names = c("dataset_index","ARI","Accuracy"))
    tkm = read.csv(paste0(type,"/var",num_var,"/var",num_var,"_c",dist2,"/final_tandem_kmeans_c",dist,"_var",num_var,"_ARI_10_PSR",PSR,".csv"), col.names = c("dataset_index","ARI","Accuracy"))
    real_gmm = read.csv(paste0(type,"/var",num_var,"/var",num_var,"_c",dist2,"/final_real_gmm_c",dist,"_var",num_var,"_ARI_10_PSR",PSR,".csv"), col.names = c("dataset_index","ARI","Accuracy")) 
    real_gmm_const = read.csv(paste0(type,"/var",num_var,"/var",num_var,"_c",dist2,"/final_real_gmm_const_c",dist,"_var",num_var,"_ARI_10_PSR",PSR,".csv"), col.names = c("dataset_index","ARI","Accuracy")) 
    
    Method = c(rep("myGMM",10), rep("1PRKM",10),rep("2RKM",10),rep("5KM",10),rep("3TKM",10),rep("GMM",10), rep("4CGMM",10))
    PSR = rep(PSR, 10 * 7)
    ho = rbind(gmm,prkm,rkm,km,tkm, real_gmm, real_gmm_const)
    return(data.frame(Method, PSR, ho[,2:3]))
}

type2_var100_c2.5 <-  filter(type2_var100_c2.5, (Method %in% c("myGMM", "GMM") == FALSE))


data = type2_var100_c2.5; num_obj = 50; num_var = 100; dist = 2.5

ggplot(data)+
    geom_boxplot(mapping = aes(x= as.factor(PSR), y = ARI, fill = Method))+
    scale_fill_grey(start = 0.3 ,end = 1, labels =c("PRKM","RKM","TKM","GMM","KM") )+
    ylim(-0.1,1)+
    theme_bw()+ 
    labs(x = "PSR", y = "ARI")+
    theme(legend.position = "bottom",legend.text=element_text(size=15),text = element_text(size=15)) 

    ggsave(file=paste0("/Users/iseunghun/Desktop/ /final_plot/Var",num_var,"_c",dist,"_num",num_obj,".jpg"))
